## Content Trusted Creators

**Question:** Whose Twitter voices should we mine for context on each
topic? One per line, format `Name | handle` (no @ symbol).

**Example answer:**
```
Paul Graham | paulg
Jason Lemkin | jasonlk
Lenny Rachitsky | lennysan
```

**If you skip:** workflow uses the 11-creator default list in
`creators.json` (tech / startups / AI). It will print the list and ask
if you want to add or remove anyone before saving.

### Answer
<!-- agent writes here -->

